===============

Description of the project
--------------------------

This project is a very simple compiler that uses the ocamllex lexing tool (lexer) as well as the menhir parsing tool (parser).

===============

Sources
-------

Git repository: https://github.com/VeganHunter/elu-610

Release : tag 1.0 or commit "latest revision"

===============

How to…
-------

…retrieve the sources?

  git clone https://github.com/VeganHunter/elu-610

…compile?

  ocamlbuild exprMain.byte

…execute and test?

  ocamlbuild exprMain.byte -- tests/testfile.pfx


===============

Structure of the project
------------------------

The project is organized as following:

project
└── _build
    ├── _digests
    ├── _log
    ├── exprMain.ml
    ├── exprMain.ml.depends
└── expr
    ├── binOp.ml
    ├── binOp.mli
    ├── exprAst.ml
    ├── exprAst.mli
    ├── exprEval.ml
    ├── exprEval.mli
    ├── exprLexer.mll
    ├── exprParser.mly
    ├── exprToPfx.ml
    ├── exprToPfx.mli
└── expr_fun
    ├── exprAst.ml
    ├── exprAst.mli
    ├── exprLexer.mll
    ├── exprParser.mly
└── pfx
    ├── pfxAst.ml
    ├── pfxEvalml
    ├── pfxEval.ml~
    ├── pfxLexer.mll
    ├── pfxParser.mly
└── tests
    ├── ex_course.pfx
    ├── ex_course1.pfx
    ├── general_test.pfx
    ├── incorrect_args_numb.pfx
    ├── incorrrect_args_numb2.pfx
    ├── push_error.pfx
    └── second.pfx
└── utils
    ├── lexingII.ml
    ├── lexingII.mli
    ├── location.ml
    └── location.mli
├── Answer_to_questions.odt
├── README
├── _tags
├── exprMain.ml
├── pfxVM.ml

